name: Cubic Dharma
desc: You take no battle damage from attacks involving "Cubic" monsters you control. During your Main Phase: You can send 1 “Cubic” card from your hand to the GY, and if you do, draw 1 card. You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 “Cubic” monster in your GY; add that monster to your hand. You can only use each of these effects of "Cubic Dharma" once per turn.
